  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast a Shinigami Clan hijutsu with the Ninjutsu keyword that doesn't have a range of self, you can choose to add your Zanpakutō as a component. When you do, the jutsu's range becomes Weapon's Range, it gains the Bukijutsu keyword, and you add your weapon's damage. You do not add your ability modifier to the damage roll(s).</p>",
